---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../scss/pages/_about.scss";
---

<BaseLayout>
    <div id="about-container">
        <div class="story">
            <h1>From Local Farms to Your Plate</h1>
            <div class="img-wrapper" style="--emoji-content: '🧑🏻‍🌾';">
                <img
                    src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5458363/pexels-photo-5458363.jpeg"
                    alt=""
                />
            </div>
            <p>
                Saffron Spice Pune was born from a simple dream: to create a
                space where Punekars could rediscover the authentic tastes of
                their childhood, presented with elegance and creativity. Our
                journey began with a commitment to our roots. We partner with
                local farmers in and around Pune to source the freshest seasonal
                produce, ensuring that every dish we serve is vibrant,
                wholesome, and bursting with natural flavor. Our name is a
                tribute to Saffron, the golden spice that symbolizes purity,
                warmth, and the rich tapestry of Indian cuisine.
            </p>
        </div>

        <section class="experience">
            <h2>More Than Just a Meal</h2>
            <div class="img-wrapper" style="--emoji-content: '🌶️';">
                <img
                    src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/25304430/pexels-photo-25304430.jpeg"
                    alt=""
                />
            </div>
            <p>
                We believe that dining is an experience that should delight all
                the senses. Our restaurant is designed to be a sanctuary from
                the hustle and bustle of city life. With warm, ambient lighting,
                comfortable seating, and decor inspired by traditional Marathi
                architecture, we've created an atmosphere that is both
                sophisticated and deeply welcoming. Whether you're here for a
                quiet lunch, a celebratory dinner, or a family gathering, our
                team is dedicated to making your visit a memorable one.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="meet-the-chef">
            <h2>Our Culinary Visionary</h2>
            <h3>Chef Aditi Rao</h3>
            <div class="img-wrapper" style="--emoji-content: '❤️';">
                <img
                    src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/9346161/pexels-photo-9346161.jpeg"
                    alt="Indian Female Chef"
                />
            </div>
            <p>
                Head Chef Aditi Rao is the heart and soul of the Saffron Spice
                kitchen. Born and raised in Pune, she combines her formal
                culinary training with the treasured recipes of her grandmother.
                Chef Aditi's philosophy is to respect the ingredients and let
                their true flavors shine. Her passion for innovation and her
                deep love for Maharashtrian food are evident in every plate that
                leaves her kitchen.
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
